# MISC::GET_TENNIS_SWING_ANIM_CAN_BE_INTERRUPTED

## Parameters
* **PED_INDEX** ped

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
If the swing anim has reached the interruptible point.
